--     * Slot: CollateralTaxonomyValue_id Description: Autocreated FK slot
--     * Slot: us_CFTC_PR_EligibleCollateral Description: Identifies US Eligible Collateral Assets classification categories based on Uncleared Margin Rules published by the CFTC and the US Prudential Regulator. Note: While the same basic categories exist in the CFTC and US Prudential Regulators’ margin rules, the precise definitions or application of those rules could differ between the two rules.
